Output docs/vhs/gotestout.gif

Require go

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontFamily "IosevkaTerm NFM"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1400
Set Height 1180
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set Framerate 30
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set BorderRadius 10
Set Margin 20
Set MarginFill "#0b1c26"

Hide
Type "cd /Users/evanschultz/Documents/Code/hylla/laslig/main && clear"
Enter
Sleep 250ms
Show

Type "go run ./examples/gotestout --format human --style always"
Enter
Sleep 4s
